How to setup ansible master node key in target nodes
two hosts master in centos, target node in ubuntu
login to master as the automation user for example a user with name ansible
run ssh-keygen to create keys
run ssh-copy-id ansible@targetIP
then ansible ping
ansible TARGET-IP-ADDRESS -m ping -u USER -vvv